The paper is about machine reading comprehension (MRC) and its focus on knowledge-based reasoning. This topic falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of external knowledge bases such as Freebase/ProBase/Reverb/NELL, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
